data.description: Beautiful one story 3BR/3.5BA residence situated on the first fairway in Boca Grove. The split bedroom plan allows for plenty of privacy and each bedroom has their own bath.  The spacious great room is perfect for entertaining and the kitchen features stainless steel appliances, island cooktop, granite counter tops and a cozy breakfast area.  The primary suite has his/her closets, a make-up area and a lavish bath.  Impact glass sliders to the back patio, a 16 KW generator, two new A/C's, a pool heater and a tankless hot water heater complete the package.  This home is also in close proximity to fine dining, great shopping and houses of worship.  Come and experience all that Boca Grove has to offer.  Boca Grove is a mandatory membership country club community.
